Axiom.name: Ax153
Axiom.Text: Class: <https://raw.github.com/ontohub/OOR_Ontohub_API/master/Domain_Fields_Core.owl#Domain_Field> Annotations: comment "The Domain Field consists of pre-defined domain-specific classes that cluster ontologies according to the domain-subject. As some ontologies cover several domains, an ontology can belong to more than one domain field. The OMV recommendation, to follow the DMOZ and ACM specifications of domain subject, is advised in those cases in which none of pre-defined fields captures the ontology subject, in which case such an ontology should be described in metadata during its upload."^^xsd:string
